subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Crystal Langhorne had 25 points and 12 rebounds to lead No. 4 Maryland to a 76-69 victory at No. 12 Duke on Sunday, hours after Terrapins Coach Brenda Frese gave birth to twin boys.
